{"type": "article", "id": 41774, "title": "这个看起来挺酷的吸入器，想纠正人们对哮喘的偏见｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-06-08T22:56:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 41281, "name": "Temper"}, {"id": 41282, "name": "123w"}, {"id": 41283, "name": "Tim Zarki"}, {"id": 41284, "name": "蔡烈超"}, {"id": 41285, "name": "Dan Rawlings"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 137, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170608215543B5EifR9ZLVrW2HvA.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Hue by Tim Zarki</h3><p>在美国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.zarki.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tim Zarki</a> 看来，医疗器械不应该与美无缘。为了纠正人们对于哮喘的偏见，在近日由设计双人组合 <a href=\"http://www.creativesession.work/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creative Session</a> 发起的 #breathebetterwithcs 设计挑战中，他带来了这款名为 Hue 的概念设计，希望能够让患病的孩子们不再羞于在公共场合使用吸入器。具有渐变效果的配色刚好与按压喷雾的操作方式形成对比，颇具时尚气息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215655sqaFOJb0yZGS1oQu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215655XMbOsRNn8ZjtSfzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215655piR6MhfrVXwqnQm4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215654wfEL0etGYHUNlj71.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>eto by Tom Cotton</h3><p>英国工业设计师 Tom Cotton 自 2011 年起就开始关注有关葡萄酒浪费的议题——有报道显示，英国每年有 5 千万升的葡萄酒因开瓶后迅速氧化造成的变味，最终被倒入下水道中。为了最大限度地减少葡萄酒与空气的接触，Cotton 研发了一款号称可以在开瓶后 12 天都不会变质的储酒器 eto，集成可拆卸硅胶真空阀的酒塞由黄铜和不锈钢制成，与玻璃瓶的组合看起来简洁优雅。无论剩下多少葡萄酒，阀门依然能够与液体紧贴，有效杜绝两者间的空气层。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/etowine/eto-a-beautiful-innovation-in-wine-preservation\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 59 英镑起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706082157176giP2odvqKN09uAT.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215716JhPz9skeMNRd6Y8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215717mBx5bfXGzQFpY3oJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215718ZrMOdpsVNJ25T1WG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.588235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215716ukfMPORDVav6TZ5N.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.697059\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nibyniebo by Justyna Wolodkiewicz</h3><p>当陶土和针线组合在一起，会诞生出怎样的创意？<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nibyniebo_/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nibyniebo</a> 是一个由波兰艺术家 Justyna Wolodkiewicz 创立的手工品牌，自学成才的她用“像是植物在纺线中生根”来形容这种奇妙的混搭。她的作品大多为以刺绣为基底的小圆箍，看上去就像是来自异世界的标本。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/uk/shop/Nibyniebo\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 50 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215749KgxvRLQHIi7BqYAa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215748lH7pR601ewYUQhrT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215748PiDqa7vNXr092KMw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215749nfLEKQcPOU9tBV73.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Flying Tables by Mario Tsai</h3><p>杭州的<a href=\"http://www.mariotsai.studio/\" rel=\"nofollow\">蔡烈超工作室</a>推出了一组名为 <a href=\"http://www.mariotsai.studio/works/flying/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flying Tables</a> 的咖啡桌，用简单的结构营造出了奇特的视觉错觉：乍看之下，金色的盘子似乎只是被放置在玻璃桌面上而已。实际上，盘子下方只有一个隐蔽的十字结构作为支撑，让人感受到一种微妙的平衡感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215922jZxgMRGTpnt3cVbf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215922o2IQNw9fgt7GcFqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706082159236BuGLTVyc2MXCmbj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.387654\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Temper by One Twenty Three West</h3><p>如果你喜欢充满艺术气息的巧克力包装，不妨来看看加拿大创意机构 <a href=\"http://123w.ca/\" rel=\"nofollow\">123w</a> 为温哥华甜品店 <a href=\"http://www.temperpastry.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Temper</a> 设计的这套新衣。这些看似用颜料随性涂抹而成的图案实际上是出自甜品店的主厨 Steven Hodge 之手的“可食用油画”，采用的原料刚好都是能够反映该款巧克力风味、颜色和质感的可可油和糖霜，巧妙地挑动人们的食欲。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215807uJkfUnNFMVvBq2c1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215806yVXFzfxpNdrtZ7e4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215807JWhDk9Ztcn4EHY8P.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215806GwWxiQFK3ZfOUg5a.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215808KRC9vt2cqXzVfDpA.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215806nUbuywTZ5cMEYHCI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nature Delivers by Dan Rawlings</h3><p>英国艺术家 <a href=\"http://everyact.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dan Rawlings</a> 擅长利用破破烂烂的金属废弃物去呈现自然界的景观，为这些物品赋予第二次生命。受英国肯德尔音乐节（<a href=\"http://www.kendalcalling.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kendal Calling</a>）委托，他为沉浸式艺术活动 <a href=\"http://www.kendalcalling.co.uk/attractions/lost-eden\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lost Eden</a> 打造了这个名为 <a href=\"http://everyact.co.uk/transit-van/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nature Delivers</a> 的装置。报废的白色货车外壳上雕满了树枝花纹，就好像是融入了绿色的树林之中。不幸的是，今年早些时候，<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BQiM1r5hPD1/\" rel=\"nofollow\">车辆因纵火</a>被毁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215957drZ61tCxiuTfO5Bc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706082159573esNzbun5IEO2lkq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170608215957O5ifzpnmFMgPCGBw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}